{"article_id":"QWW2cQcw8MTaRMUg","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Senate Majority Leader Mitch McConnell now has the support","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"to move forward with a partisan vote","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"establishing the rules for the impeachment trial ,","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"an update","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"he made clear earlier this week .","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"But House Speaker Nancy Pelosi isn ' t blinking just yet .","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"Pelosi on Tuesday emphasized","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"that she will not send over the House articles of impeachment for President Donald Trump","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"until she sees the Senate protocol for the trial in writing , the latest move","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"she ' s made","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"to dig in on her position .","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"Previously , Pelosi ' s decision","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"to withhold the articles","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"- which are needed","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"in order for the Senate to begin the trial -","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"was seen as an effort","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"to pressure the Senate to come up with what Democrats viewed as a fair approach .","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"The trial , after all , will determine","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"whether Trump is ultimately convicted and removed from office over his attempts","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"to coerce Ukraine into investigating his political opponent .","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"Back in December , it was unclear if all Republicans","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"- particularly a trio of swing senators -","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"would back McConnell","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"in advancing a rules package along partisan lines from the get-go .","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"By hanging on to the articles ,","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"Pelosi could both hammer Republicans with negative messaging about their decision","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"to not immediately call witnesses for the trial","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"and buy more time","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"to pressure this group of pivotal moderates .","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"These swing senators , however , have since indicated","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"that they stand with McConnell .","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"And some Senate Democrats have started urging her to transmit the articles .","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"\" I think","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"the time has passed .","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"She should send the articles over , \"","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"Sen. Chris Murphy","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"( D-CT )","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"recently told the Washington Post .","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"Pelosi is still building the argument against the GOP-controlled Senate ' s handling of trial process","depth":5},{"id":39,"text":"- to mixed success","depth":5},{"id":40,"text":"The speaker ,","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"who has kept her cards close to the vest for the entire impeachment process ,","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"is reportedly even tighter-lipped about her strategy for the articles .","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"As CNN ' s Manu Raju wrote earlier this week ,","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"Pelosi had , at one point , not told Senate Minority Leader Chuck Schumer or her \" closest confidantes \" about her plans .","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"When she does discuss it ,","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"she ' s pressed the Senate to offer concrete commitments .","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"On Tuesday , she said","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"she ' s still waiting on the rule specifics from the upper chamber","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"before transferring anything ,","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"though McConnell has chafed at this request .","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"There will be no haggling with the House over Senate procedure .","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"We will not cede our authority","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"to try this impeachment .","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"The House Democrats ' turn is over .","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"The Senate has made its decision .","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"This is for the Senate , and the Senate only , to decide .","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"- Leader McConnell","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"( @ senatemajldr )","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"January 8 , 2020","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"\" It is important that he immediately publish this resolution ,","depth":5},{"id":61,"text":"so that ,","depth":7},{"id":62,"text":"as I have said before ,","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"we can see the arena","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"in which we will be participating ,","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"appoint managers","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"and transmit the articles to the Senate , \"","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"Pelosi wrote in a letter to her House colleagues on Tuesday .","depth":6},{"id":68,"text":"Getting these rules in writing","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"- as unlikely as that prospect might be -","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"would enable the House to have a better sense","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"of how its impeachment managers will have to operate","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"as the trial unfolds ,","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"former Pelosi Chief of Staff John Lawrence told .","depth":7},{"id":74,"text":"Although the trial takes place in the Senate ,","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"the House will continue to have a central role ,","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"he said ,","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"seeing as how House members will effectively be serving as the prosecution .","depth":7},{"id":78,"text":"But there are a couple of other factors at play , too .","depth":6},{"id":79,"text":"A House Democratic leadership aide noted","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"that some of Pelosi ' s reasons","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"for holding the articles in the first place","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"still stand .","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"For one :","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"Since the House ' s impeachment vote in December , more and more documents","depth":14},{"id":85,"text":"- including Pentagon emails about Ukraine aid -","depth":14},{"id":86,"text":"have leaked out","depth":13},{"id":87,"text":"and strengthened Democrats ' case ,","depth":13},{"id":88,"text":"further building the public record for the Trump impeachment charges .","depth":13},{"id":89,"text":"Depending on how long she keeps the articles ,","depth":13},{"id":90,"text":"it ' s possible even more information will emerge","depth":14},{"id":91,"text":"that makes Republicans ' take on trial procedure look even worse . \"","depth":14},{"id":92,"text":"[ Former National Security Adviser John ] Bolton ' s statement on Monday and new emails","depth":17},{"id":93,"text":"showing","depth":18},{"id":94,"text":"the Pentagon was concerned about President Trump ' s freeze on Ukraine aid","depth":18},{"id":95,"text":"are significant developments","depth":16},{"id":96,"text":"that demand a fair trial in the Senate","depth":15},{"id":97,"text":"- and wouldn ' t have happened","depth":15},{"id":98,"text":"without Speaker Pelosi holding the articles , \"","depth":15},{"id":99,"text":"the aide says .","depth":13},{"id":100,"text":"Additionally , this extra time has meant","depth":12},{"id":101,"text":"that Democrats can continue to press Republicans about what they see as a \" sham \" trial , an effort","depth":13},{"id":102,"text":"likely aimed at shifting public opinion on the issue .","depth":13},{"id":103,"text":"It ' s not clear how successful that push is .","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"In December , before the holiday break , 54 percent of voters favored the Senate","depth":14},{"id":105,"text":"calling more witnesses for the impeachment trial ,","depth":14},{"id":106,"text":"according to Morning Consult ;","depth":13},{"id":107,"text":"57 percent of voters did in January ,","depth":13},{"id":108,"text":"marking only a slight uptick .","depth":13},{"id":109,"text":"( A separate poll from LawWorks recently found","depth":12},{"id":110,"text":"that 67 percent of voters in six battleground states were interested in a full trial with fair consideration of the evidence versus a speedy acquittal . )","depth":12},{"id":111,"text":"Trump himself has seemed distressed by the delay ,","depth":10},{"id":112,"text":"if the number of tweets","depth":12},{"id":113,"text":"he shared about it over the holidays","depth":12},{"id":114,"text":"is any indication .","depth":11},{"id":115,"text":"Even so , the growing Senate comments from Pelosi ' s party signal","depth":11},{"id":116,"text":"that the pressure is increasing on the speaker to send the articles ,","depth":11},{"id":117,"text":"prompting some to speculate","depth":11},{"id":118,"text":"that it could happen soon .","depth":11},{"id":119,"text":"Still , it remains to be seen just how long she ' s willing to wait for the assurances","depth":10},{"id":120,"text":"she ' s interested in getting from the Senate .","depth":10},{"id":121,"text":"\" Mrs . Pelosi plays three-dimensional checkers","depth":12},{"id":122,"text":"and sometimes it takes a while to figure out all the moves , \"","depth":12},{"id":123,"text":"says Lawrence .","depth":11},{"id":124,"text":"\" I ' d be very surprised","depth":12},{"id":125,"text":"if she wants there to be a lengthy delay ,","depth":12},{"id":126,"text":"but she ' s not going to telescope her endgame . \"","depth":11},{"id":127,"text":"There has been growing pressure for Pelosi to turn over the articles soon ,","depth":5},{"id":128,"text":"though House Democrats are still backing her strategy","depth":5},{"id":129,"text":"A handful of Senate Democrats have joined Republicans in the push","depth":6},{"id":130,"text":"for Pelosi to transmit the articles ,","depth":6},{"id":131,"text":"as lawmakers get antsy about completing a trial .","depth":5},{"id":132,"text":"House members , meanwhile , emphasized","depth":6},{"id":133,"text":"that they backed her efforts","depth":7},{"id":134,"text":"to raise awareness about the partisan nature of the Senate process .","depth":7},{"id":135,"text":"\" She is right to highlight what some of the Republicans ,","depth":10},{"id":136,"text":"including the [ House majority ]","depth":11},{"id":137,"text":"leader ,","depth":11},{"id":138,"text":"have said ,","depth":9},{"id":139,"text":"which is anything but impartial , \"","depth":8},{"id":140,"text":"Rep. Gerry Connolly , a member of the House Oversight Committee , told .","depth":7},{"id":141,"text":"\" When the Senate majority leader says","depth":9},{"id":142,"text":"there will be basically no daylight between his coordination with the White House ,","depth":10},{"id":143,"text":"as it pertains to the process ,","depth":10},{"id":144,"text":"I think","depth":9},{"id":145,"text":"the speaker was absolutely correct to hold on to the articles of impeachment","depth":10},{"id":146,"text":"until we know what the rules are , \"","depth":10},{"id":147,"text":"Rep. Val Demings , a House Judiciary member , added .","depth":7},{"id":148,"text":"Pelosi ' s decision","depth":8},{"id":149,"text":"to keep the articles","depth":8},{"id":150,"text":"has shifted the expected Senate timeline somewhat .","depth":7},{"id":151,"text":"Based on the original plans ,","depth":7},{"id":152,"text":"there was a sense","depth":8},{"id":153,"text":"the trial could start as early as January 6","depth":9},{"id":154,"text":"and run for most of the month .","depth":9},{"id":155,"text":"Given the delay around the articles ,","depth":7},{"id":156,"text":"it ' s now uncertain when it will kick off ,","depth":7},{"id":157,"text":"as the 2020 presidential primary looms in the background .","depth":6},{"id":158,"text":"Murphy hasn ' t been the only Democrat","depth":7},{"id":159,"text":"to express his concerns ,","depth":7},{"id":160,"text":"Politico reports .","depth":6},{"id":161,"text":"Others ,","depth":9},{"id":162,"text":"including Sen. Dianne Feinstein","depth":10},{"id":163,"text":"( D-CA ) ,","depth":10},{"id":164,"text":"have suggested","depth":8},{"id":165,"text":"the delay is undercutting the urgency of the impeachment process ,","depth":8},{"id":166,"text":"as Democrats ' leverage wanes .","depth":8},{"id":167,"text":"\" If it ' s serious and urgent ,","depth":9},{"id":168,"text":"send them over .","depth":9},{"id":169,"text":"If it isn ' t ,","depth":9},{"id":170,"text":"don ' t send it over , \"","depth":9},{"id":171,"text":"Feinstein told Politico .","depth":7},{"id":172,"text":"The timing around the articles is still unknown ,","depth":5},{"id":173,"text":"as both chambers also continue to grapple with the recent US airstrike","depth":7},{"id":174,"text":"that killed Iranian official Qassem Soleimani","depth":7},{"id":175,"text":"and the Iranian response .","depth":6},{"id":176,"text":"While there have been questions","depth":6},{"id":177,"text":"about whether Pelosi might hold on to the articles indefinitely ,","depth":6},{"id":178,"text":"this outcome doesn ' t feel particularly likely .","depth":5},{"id":179,"text":"\" She ' s a big believer in process ,","depth":6},{"id":180,"text":"and that leads me to suggest","depth":7},{"id":181,"text":"she would send them over sooner rather than later , \"","depth":7},{"id":182,"text":"Jim Manley , a Democratic strategist and former staffer for Senate Majority Leader Harry Reid , told .","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":365,"left":309,"right":364,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":309,"left":220,"right":308,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":220,"left":193,"right":219,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":193,"left":187,"right":192,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":187,"left":185,"right":186,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":185,"left":0,"right":184,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":184,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"p